properties.name: detour5
properties.description: Detour #5: Marathon miles 8 + 9: Piedmont From 8:00am to 10:15am: To get to Montclair Village, head up Moraga to Highway 13 southbound, exit at Joaquin Miller/Lincoln, take left over Highway 13, left on Mountain Blvd. to return to Village. Or take a left back to Highway 13 northbound to get to Highway 24 or I-580. Of special note: Vehicles coming from the Piedmont side of La Salle will need to turn right on Estates to Park Blvd. and then down to I-580 OR left on Estates to Moraga. After 10:15am: Runners will have cleared area; streets will be reopened to normal traffic.
